{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十二回：老衲山中移漏处　佳人世外改妆时\n\n本章主要讲述韦小宝离京前往少林寺途中的遭遇。他带领骁骑营出京，在途中扎营时与众军官赌博取乐。王屋派弟子司徒鹤、曾柔等人突然袭击军营，杀死侍卫葛通。韦小宝与敌人掷骰赌头，凭借机智和匕首反败为胜，擒获元义方。通过审讯得知王屋派意图绑架吴三桂之子吴应熊，以此要挟吴三桂造反。韦小宝故意将此事攀诬到吴三桂头上，派人向康熙密奏。康熙却下密旨斥责他诬陷功臣，令他不得再提此事。\n\n韦小宝抵达少林寺后，被康熙安排代帝出家，法名晦明。他在寺中遇到两名神秘少女，绿衫女郎面容绝美，令他一见倾心。两少女与寺僧发生冲突，韦小宝在冲突中无意抓住绿衫女郎胸口，导致对方羞愤自刎，幸被老僧所救。般若堂首座澄观分析两少女武功为偷学各派杂拌儿。韦小宝为了接近绿衫女郎，诱使澄观研究武功速成之法。他在潭头铺妓院再次遇到两少女，险些被杀，狼狈逃回少林寺。本章展现了韦小宝的机智狡黠、好色多情，以及少林寺的武功体系。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_xian",
      "speaker_name": "赵齐贤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "葛通！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_he",
      "speaker_name": "司徒鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那还用问？输剑赔剑，输头赔头！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "成了！美女吹气，有杀无赔！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乌龟王八蛋才怕！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放开便放开，有什么希奇？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放下银子，我就饶了你们的头儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！小姑娘，你先掷！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你姓元，叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，干了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那怎猜得到？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父吩咐，命我们想法子擒了他去王屋山，以此要挟吴三桂，迫他⋯⋯迫他⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "共有四百多人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总有二千来人罢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是，是，有九千多人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_chun",
      "speaker_name": "富春",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，还得狠狠的打。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像⋯⋯好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也不太远。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人数多得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "元义方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有些⋯⋯有些小人不大清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见者有份，人人都有功劳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_kang_nian",
      "speaker_name": "张康年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说平西王造反，不知道够不够证据？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请三位去跟师爷商量一下，怎么写这道奏章。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_cong",
      "speaker_name": "晦聪禅师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师弟，拜过了如来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 996,
      "line_end": 996
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_ji",
      "speaker_name": "净济",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1004,
      "line_end": 1004
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那蓝衫姑娘先将四个⋯⋯四个和尚都打断了手⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1062,
      "line_end": 1062
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这个高僧马马虎虎，随便凑数，当不得真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1110,
      "line_end": 1110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_guan",
      "speaker_name": "澄观",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是，是。师叔，咱们出去罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1254,
      "line_end": 1254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_guan",
      "speaker_name": "澄观",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是'一指禅'功夫，师叔不会吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1288,
      "line_end": 1288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎样弹法？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1302,
      "line_end": 1302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那倒好玩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1304,
      "line_end": 1304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "般若掌我也不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1310,
      "line_end": 1310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你开始学武，到练成一指禅，花了多少时候？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1354,
      "line_end": 1354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你从十一岁练起，到了五十三岁时略跪什么门闩（他不知",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1360,
      "line_end": 1360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女施主的伤处好些了吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1448,
      "line_end": 1448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_xiao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "韦小宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "问什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1676,
      "line_end": 1676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_ji",
      "speaker_name": "净济",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说不是呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1696,
      "line_end": 1696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_guan",
      "speaker_name": "澄观",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是啊，所以这就奇怪了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1742,
      "line_end": 1742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_guan",
      "speaker_name": "澄观",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 1786,
      "line_end": 1786
    }
